article_id:1828,category_name:News,title_name:Daily Free Tenfold Summon Incoming!,image_path:,message:<div>A daily free tenfold summon event, which will allow you to perform a tenfold summon on the applicable summon showcase for free once per day, will be live for the following durations!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div>・Part One</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1609394400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1609739999"></span></div><div><br></div><div>・Part Two</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1609999200"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1610258399"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■Applicable Summon Showcase</div><div>You can perform a tenfold summon on one the following summon showcases for free once per day according to the schedule above.</div><div><br></div><div>・Cursed Connections (Part One)</div><div>Note: You can perform up to four tenfold summons during the four-day period from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1609394400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1609739999"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>・Cursed Connections (Part Two)</div><div>Note: You can perform up to three tenfold summons during the three-day period from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1609999200"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1610258399"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. You can perform a tenfold summon for free on the applicable summon showcase once per day (each day is from 6:00 AM to 5:59 AM the next day).</div><div>2. The daily free tenfold summon resets each day at 6:00 AM.</div><div>3. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1609135200,update_time1608807504